            "highlight": "When, and",
            "keywords": "opened it, great cloud came out",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p2",
        "text": "'Prepare to die!' shouted the genie.",
        "emoji": "😠",
        "keywords": "Prepare to die, shouted",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p2_1",
            "text": "'A long time ago, I made a promise.'",
