            "emoji": "💰",
            "highlight": "If",
            "keywords": "set me free, rich and powerful",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p2_3",
            "text": "'But no one ever came.'",
            "emoji": "😔",
            "highlight": "But",
            "keywords": "no one came",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p3",
        "text": "'After years and years of waiting, I became very angry.'",
        "emoji": "😡",
        "highlight": "After",
